data.description: Welcome to your dream home at 20305 W Peak View Rd! This exceptional property offers the perfect blend of space, style, and versatility. With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this stunning residence boasts a spacious 3,211 sq ft of living space, making it a haven for comfortable living and entertaining. Taxes show 2011. The improvements are evident throughout, from the newly painted cabinets in the kitchen and baths to the new countertops and fresh paint that enhance the overall appeal. So many upgrades the owner has provided a list in attachments. One of the standout features of this property is the expansive 4-car attached garage, Additionally, a separate 2-car garage offers even more parking and storage options.
